query:
select c.address
                        from nft_collection c
                        left join meta_handled_addresses mha on mha.address = c.address
                        where
                            /*c.verified and*/
                            (mha.address is null)
                            or (mha.updated_at < (extract(epoch from now()) - $2)::bigint and failed)
                        order by updated desc
                        limit $1
